In the paper, a mixed problem for $\lambda $-complex parameter dependent, fourth order partial equation is considered. The estimations for the Green function for the eigenvalues of the considered problem outside of $\delta $ were obtained within the regular boundary condition. The solution of the mixed problem was given in theÂ contour integral form.
